snippet.title: Indoor Playground Family Fun Play Area for kids playing with Ice Cream Toys for Children
snippet.description:
Indoor Playground for kids are the latest trend that hit Jogjakarta since there are lot of places to play with your children on the week end. Located in one of the biggest mall in Yogyakarta, Hartono Mall, the indoor playground are so colorful and attractive.

All of the toys are complete since they have giant slides, ball pit, seesaw, kitchen utensils that are so interesting for your kids to play with.

Admission:
Weekday : IDR 45K (1 hour)
Weekend : IDR 90K (1 hour)

Happy Playing, kids!

snippet.title: Indoor Playground For Kids - McDonald's Family Fun on Slides with Chase and Cole Adventures
snippet.description:
Indoor Playground For Kids - McDonald's Family Fun on Slides with Chase and Cole Adventures. Thank you for watching our Family Channel!

Afternoon filled with fun, Happy Meals, slides and prizes! The McDonalds playground is a staple for Chase and Cole when the weather is bad and we need to get them out of the house and moving. Nothing is better than burning off some energy and then eating a Happy Meal! We love visiting our local McDonalds and having fun at its indoor playground.

SUBSCRIBE FOR MORE YOUTUBE KIDS VIDEOS 😀

https://bit.ly/2DID85td

ABOUT CHASE AND COLE ADVENTURES 😀🎢🎡🚂🦖
 
Welcome to our family channel, Chase and Cole Adventures, where Chase and Cole want to be your friends so they can help make your day a fun-filled adventure. If you're looking for entertaining, safe and family friendly content then subscribe now and have your family Join the Adventure!
 
We really want to provide you with videos your family will enjoy watching, so we go beyond unboxing toys and doing the traditional toy review videos, by taking you, and the cool toys, on their very own Adventure. Whether it's trips to Amusement Parks, the beach, a fun game of tag, gameplay of our favorite video games, pretend play or one of our awesome rescue missions, Chase and Cole want to bring you on their Adventures and have you experience all the fun that's possible with the latest new toys.
 
We will be posting NEW videos to our kids channel every Thursday, Friday, Saturday and Sunday.
